'''Minestrone of Rice and Cabbage'''
Ingredients: * Rice * cabbage * stock * ham * tomato sauce.
Cut off the stalk and all the hard outside leaves of a cabbage, wash it and cut it up, but not too small, then drain and cook it in good stock and add two ounces of boiled rice. This minestrone is improved by adding a little chopped ham and a few spoonsful of tomato sauce.
