== Procedure == # Plump dried fruit in juice. # Mash reconstituted fruit with almond and spices to get a mortar-like texture. # Adjust texture with matsoh meal and if needed, sweeten with honey. # Serve as part of the [[Cookbook:Seder|Seder]]. The North-West African tradition uses bitter greens such as endive rather than horseradish with the Charoseth.
